  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1276730/" class="title-link">舒服的落后状态</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1276730"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zyb/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2151558-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zyb/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">册子婆婆</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-01-08"
      class="main-meta">2008-01-08 10:23:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1276730_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不同于君主专制，我非常喜欢“绝对主义”国家这个翻译term。形式上优于传统君主制的专制体制在普遍意义上对于一个国家的初建极其有利，可是可怕的事情是：当一个统治者或者一个政党已经习惯于被崇拜和被忠于执行的时候，他们会忘记掉向“现代”前行这件事情。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1276730/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
