            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36908545">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">中译：军事机构在俄国的角色远不如在普鲁士

原文：The role of the military apparatus in Russia, on the other hand, was scarcely less great than in Prussia.

纠正：俄国的军事机构几乎同普鲁士的一样重要。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-03 21:00</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                中译：军事机构在俄国的角色远不如在普鲁士<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>原文：The role of the military apparatus in Russia, on the other hand, was scarcely less great than in Prussia.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>纠正：俄国的军事机构几乎同普鲁士的一样重要。
